 4.7 VSRC - Independent Voltage Source

     Ver:    N/A
     Class:  V
     Level:  1 (and only)
     Dir:    devices/vsrc
     Status:

     This is the original spice device improved by Alan Gillespie
     with the following features:

     - Source ramping
     - Check for non-monotonic series in PWL


