      (but EPFL is not publishing any usefull code)


 13.2 PSP MOS Model

      Ver:    102.1
      Level:  45
      Dir:    devices/adms/psp102
      Status: TO BE TESTED

      Philips SimKit 2.5.


 13.3 HICUM0 Bipolar Model

      Ver:    Level_0 Version_1.12
      Level:  7
