      Status: TO BE TESTED

      A simplified version of HICUM Level2 model for BJT
      Web site at: http://www.iee.et.tu-dresden.de/iee/eb/hic_new


 13.4 HICUM2 Bipolar Model

      Ver:    Level_2 Version_2.22
      Level:  8
      Dir:    devices/adms/hicum2
